      "body": "<p>I have been trying to maintain a <a href=\"http://jewelcli.lexicalscope.com/related.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">list of Java CLI parsers</a>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/airlift/airline\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><strong>Airline</strong></a>\n<ul>\n<li>Active Fork: <a href=\"https://github.com/rvesse/airline\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://github.com/rvesse/airline</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/tatsuhiro-t/argparse4j\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><strong>argparse4j</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.cs.ubc.ca/spider/lloyd/java/argparser.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><strong>argparser</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://args4j.kohsuke.org/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><strong>args4j</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://clajr.sourceforge.net/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><strong>clajr</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://code.google.com/p/cli-parser/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><strong>cli-parser</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://ostermiller.org/utils/CmdLn.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><strong>CmdLn</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/jankroken/commandline\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><strong>Commandline</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/tomitribe/crest\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><strong>crest</strong></a>: Command-line API styled after JAX-RS</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/docopt/docopt.java\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><strong>DocOpt.java</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://dolphin.sourceforge.net/getopt/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><strong>dolphin getopt</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.dpml.net/util/cli/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><strong>DPML CLI (Jakarta Commons CLI2 fork)</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.javaworld.com/javaworld/jw-08-2004/jw-0816-command.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><strong>Dr. Matthias Laux</strong></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://jakart